1
00:00:03,250 --> 00:00:05,000
No matter how much
you hate me,

2
00:00:05,830 --> 00:00:07,420
I'm still crazy about you.

3
00:00:08,460 --> 00:00:10,630
Just get on your knees,
and this will all be over.

4
00:00:11,630 --> 00:00:13,460
That's a pretty good deal, isn't it?

5
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:16,880
Yes.

6
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:25,380
You've been embezzling company funds.

7
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:27,080
You wouldn't want that to get out, would you?

8
00:00:27,710 --> 00:00:30,130
Spending a fortune
on male escorts and all that.

9
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:35,630
What should I do?

10
00:00:37,420 --> 00:00:39,540
I need you to
make a big scene.

11
00:00:41,670 --> 00:00:43,250
Get on your knees, now!

12
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:45,420
What are you spacing out for?

13
00:00:46,790 --> 00:00:47,420
Hurry up!

14
00:00:47,710 --> 00:00:49,750
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

15
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:52,210
Hurry up!!

16
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:02,920
This... Did you
put something in here?

17
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:04,580
This is...

18
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:08,460
Huh? What?

19
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:11,580
This is...
What is going on?

20
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:13,790
Who would put something like this...

21
00:01:14,130 --> 00:01:16,290
No, I didn't do this.

22
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,290
Ma'am, I've had enough.

23
00:01:19,380 --> 00:01:20,960
Just kidding.

24
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,630
Everyone, this was just part of the entertainment.

25
00:01:23,380 --> 00:01:24,830
It was just for entertainment.

26
00:01:25,380 --> 00:01:27,000
Ma'am.

27
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:28,420
Please, help me.

28
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:30,920
Everyone, I apologize for the disturbance.

29
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,250
I'm truly sorry.

30
00:01:32,290 --> 00:01:33,750
Part of the entertainment...

31
00:01:36,670 --> 00:01:38,630
That's not what this was at all.

32
00:01:38,630 --> 00:01:40,130
I don't know
what her reasons were,

33
00:01:40,130 --> 00:01:41,670
but she staged this whole thing herself.

34
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,130
That's not true.

35
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:44,710
I would never do something like this...

36
00:01:59,170 --> 00:02:00,380
My hand slipped.
